task.summary: Added POST request functionality for adding tasks
Fixed GET request to retrieve specific task information.
Added a timer that runs when you start a task.
Added PATCH and DELETE endpoints; made it so 'completed' field cannot be set on POST.
When the timer runs out, the task is now marked complete and removed from the list
Added global settings model; modified point values to relate to global settings
Added token-based authentication backend; not used in front end just yet
